traditions for dying.

00:35:23.680 --> 00:35:25.930 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, and anyone who
went through that process,

00:35:25.930 --> 00:35:27.790 align:middle line:84%
please know that I'm
not making it wrong.

00:35:27.790 --> 00:35:33.568 align:middle line:84%
I'm just looking at the entire
would-- a dear friend of ours

00:35:33.568 --> 00:35:35.110 align:middle line:84%
who went through
this process with us

00:35:35.110 --> 00:35:37.960 align:middle line:84%
