00:35:41.560 --> 00:35:43.320 align:middle line:90%
The velvet inside the coffin.

00:35:43.320 --> 00:35:44.120 align:middle line:90%
I mean--

00:35:44.120 --> 00:35:45.037 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: Absolutely.

00:35:45.037 --> 00:35:46.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: --it brought
him pleasure.

00:35:46.540 --> 00:35:47.680 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: Absolutely.

00:35:47.680 --> 00:35:50.575 align:middle line:84%
And different traditions
require different things.

00:35:50.575 --> 00:35:51.766 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mhm.

00:35:51.766 --> 00:35:55.030 align:middle line:84%
>>EDWARDS: So it's
really making your ritual

00:35:55.030 --> 00:35:57.440 align:middle line:90%
true to your values.

00:35:57.440 --> 00:35:58.240 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:35:58.240 --> 00:35:59.030 align:middle line:90%
And whatever works for you.

00:35:59.030 --> 00:36:00.430 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't have to be perfect.

00:36:00.430 --> 00:36:01.240 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: No.

00:36:01.240 --> 00:36:02.865 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But can we
go back to that idea

00:36:02.865 --> 00:36:05.740 align:middle line:84%
of living without any
regrets, no regrets.

00:36:05.740 --> 00:36:07.880 align:middle line:84%
You have a whole foundation
called the No Regrets

00:36:07.880 --> 00:36:08.680 align:middle line:90%
Foundation.

00:36:08.680 --> 00:36:10.097 align:middle line:10%
>>EDWARDS: Right,
that was started

00:36:10.097 --> 00:36:14.020 align:middle line:10%
by Patti Panza, who created
the project in the last six

00:36:14.020 --> 00:36:15.400 align:middle line:10%
months of her life.

00:36:15.400 --> 00:36:17.080 align:middle line:90%
This is her legacy.

00:36:17.080 --> 00:36:21.760 align:middle line:84%
And she developed five
practices she thought

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:26.720 align:middle line:84%
would help her get to her
deathbed with no regrets.

00:36:26.720 --> 00:36:27.520 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:36:27.520 --> 00:36:29.680 align:middle line:84%
>>EDWARDS: And so she shared
it with everyone else.

00:36:29.680 --> 00:36:33.950 align:middle line:10%
And those practices are
be grateful every day,

00:36:33.950 --> 00:36:39.440 align:middle line:10%
choose joy, trust,
and take the risk,

00:36:39.440 --> 00:36:44.480 align:middle line:10%
have the courage to be
yourself, and love yourself

00:36:44.480 --> 00:36:48.330 align:middle line:10%
first, and then share it.

00:36:48.330 --> 00:36:49.130 align:middle line:90%
That's a hard one.

00:36:49.130 --> 00:36:50.450 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's the hardest one.

00:36:50.450 --> 00:36:54.050 align:middle line:84%
>>EDWARDS: Meaning that if
you give everything away,

00:36:54.050 --> 00:36:55.640 align:middle line:84%
you will have
nothing left to give.

00:36:55.640 --> 00:36:57.560 align:middle line:90%
So love yourself first.

00:36:57.560 --> 00:37:00.590 align:middle line:84%
And we don't-- caregivers have
a very hard time with that

00:37:00.590 --> 00:37:03.960 align:middle line:90%
because they have so much to do.

00:37:03.960 --> 00:37:04.760 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:37:04.760 --> 00:37:05.720 align:middle line:90%
Constantly.

00:37:05.720 --> 00:37:06.520 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: Yeah.

00:37:06.520 --> 00:37:08.090 align:middle line:84%
So for caregivers,
it's that, you

00:37:08.090 --> 00:37:12.653 align:middle line:84%
know, OK, step back, take care
of yourself, and then share it.

00:37:12.653 --> 00:37:14.570 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That was the
hardest thing for my mom,

00:37:14.570 --> 00:37:17.030 align:middle line:84%
because she was
constantly tugged.

00:37:17.030 --> 00:37:19.500 align:middle line:84%
If she wasn't at the
hospital, she felt guilty.

00:37:19.500 --> 00:37:21.740 align:middle line:84%
When she was at the
hospital, she felt guilty.

00:37:21.740 --> 00:37:23.990 align:middle line:84%
Trying to make the phone
calls of all the preparations

00:37:23.990 --> 00:37:25.773 align:middle line:90%
for hospice or whatnot.

00:37:25.773 --> 00:37:27.440 align:middle line:84%
Any moment she wasn't
with him-- and me,

00:37:27.440 --> 00:37:30.800 align:middle line:84%
