father, every moment, who

00:37:30.800 --> 00:37:33.170 align:middle line:84%
am I to be working,
what am I thinking.

00:37:33.170 --> 00:37:36.900 align:middle line:84%
I should be spending
every moment with him.

00:37:36.900 --> 00:37:40.080 align:middle line:84%
And what would you tell
people dealing with that?

00:37:40.080 --> 00:37:42.350 align:middle line:90%
I still haven't resolved that.

00:37:42.350 --> 00:37:43.940 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: Do you have a regret?

00:37:43.940 --> 00:37:46.310 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: The only
regret I have is,

00:37:46.310 --> 00:37:48.860 align:middle line:84%
towards the last
days of his life,

00:37:48.860 --> 00:37:52.670 align:middle line:84%
I could see energetically
he was not there.

00:37:52.670 --> 00:37:57.830 align:middle line:84%
And I intuitively knew
he was at the end.

00:37:57.830 --> 00:38:00.230 align:middle line:90%
And I went into an anger.

00:38:00.230 --> 00:38:02.760 align:middle line:84%
I'm like, what
are we doing here?

00:38:02.760 --> 00:38:07.310 align:middle line:84%
And I regret that, because now
I look back, and that's a stage,

00:38:07.310 --> 00:38:09.320 align:middle line:90%
it's a normal stage.

00:38:09.320 --> 00:38:12.410 align:middle line:84%
And I'm such a doer, I'm
like, what are we doing here?

00:38:12.410 --> 00:38:16.100 align:middle line:90%
And I am ashamed of that.

00:38:16.100 --> 00:38:19.372 align:middle line:84%
Like, what do you mean,
what are you doing here?

00:38:19.372 --> 00:38:20.580 align:middle line:90%
Like, what are we doing, Dad?

00:38:20.580 --> 00:38:21.590 align:middle line:90%
What are we doing, Dad?

00:38:21.590 --> 00:38:23.330 align:middle line:90%
Come on.

00:38:23.330 --> 00:38:26.210 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't like that, but
it was in my own mind

00:38:26.210 --> 00:38:27.260 align:middle line:90%
I was saying that.

00:38:27.260 --> 00:38:29.040 align:middle line:90%
And I was looking at my dad.

00:38:29.040 --> 00:38:31.130 align:middle line:84%
And everybody's talking
and having conversations,

00:38:31.130 --> 00:38:32.750 align:middle line:90%
and there's my dad dying.

00:38:32.750 --> 00:38:36.140 align:middle line:84%
And it was so surreal
that I-- and I

00:38:36.140 --> 00:38:39.350 align:middle line:84%
