were blowing up at work.

00:38:39.350 --> 00:38:42.200 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, this
is too surreal.

00:38:42.200 --> 00:38:43.070 align:middle line:90%
This is wrong.

00:38:43.070 --> 00:38:45.410 align:middle line:84%
Something about this
moment is wrong.

00:38:45.410 --> 00:38:48.050 align:middle line:84%
And then I stopped
everybody, and I said, look,

00:38:48.050 --> 00:38:51.560 align:middle line:90%
this is just too surreal.

00:38:51.560 --> 00:38:54.020 align:middle line:84%
I have the laptop, and the
nurse is talking about what type

00:38:54.020 --> 00:38:56.180 align:middle line:84%
