with, and someone over there

00:38:56.180 --> 00:38:56.980 align:middle line:90%
is on the phone.

00:38:56.980 --> 00:38:58.550 align:middle line:90%
And I'm like, ugh.

00:38:58.550 --> 00:38:59.623 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, I had a moment.

00:38:59.623 --> 00:39:01.040 align:middle line:84%
I have a regret
about that moment.

00:39:01.040 --> 00:39:01.640 align:middle line:90%
>>EDWARDS: OK.

